Manipulation of Belgium Catches

BEdata<- fish_catch %>%
  gather(year, count, X2014:X2013:X2012:X2011:X2010:X2009:X2008:X2007:X2006)
BE_catch<-BEdata%>%
  select(year,count)
new_BE<-BE_catch%>%
  group_by(year)%>%
  summarize(count=sum(count))
knitr::kable(new_BE)
